parameter.SemanticDefinition:
This enumerated parameter reports on the subcarrier lock status of the BPSK subcarrier demodulator. The values the parameter may have are:
- 'locked' - the demodulator has locked on the return link subcarrier;
- 'not-locked' - the demodulator has not locked on the return link subcarrier and therefore cannot deliver telemetry.

This enumerated parameter reports the subcarrier wave form. The values the parameter may have are:
- 'sine' - the subcarrier is a sinusodial wave;
- 'square' - the subcarrier is a square wave.
